<h1>About</h1>
<p>
  This application demonstrates how you can easily instrument your rails app to build
  and share live monitoring dashboards with <%= link_to 'Regrapher', 'https://www.regrapher.com', target: '_blank' -%>.
</p>
<p>
  <strong>
    Here is a sample shared (read-only)
    <%= link_to 'dashboard', 'https://www.regrapher.com/shared_dashboards/dWX8UONeDHoXaLq51M5ccI8heMgsCw4LpgTD6z3F', target: '_blank' %>
    monitoring this application activity in real-time.
  </strong>
</p>
<div class="well well-lg">
  <p>
    It is not necessary to create an account just to test how the dashboard updates in real-time. Visiting
    <%= link_to 'this page', about_page_path %> and pushing the button below will update the <em>About Page</em> and
    the <em>About Button</em> widgets of the
    <%= link_to 'dashboard', 'https://www.regrapher.com/shared_dashboards/dWX8UONeDHoXaLq51M5ccI8heMgsCw4LpgTD6z3F', target: '_blank' %>.
  </p>
  <p>
    <%= link_to 'About Button', about_button_path, remote: true, method: :post, class: 'btn btn-lg btn-danger', data: { disable_with: 'About Button' } %>
  </p>
</div>
<p>
  This application is open source and is available
  at <%= link_to 'github', 'https://github.com/regrapher/regrapher-example-app-rails-4', target: '_blank' -%>.
</p>

